window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Once Upon A Time,</p> <p>there was a wicked girl.</p> <p>She lost everything that mattered,</p> <p>causing darkness to unfurl.</p> <p>Impulsive and intelligent,</p> <p>she helped her family name grow strong.</p> <p>But then one day a man without a heart came along.</p> <p>An undercover agent, meant to spy and bring back tips.</p> <p>Following down her hidden path of faded yellow bricks.</p> <p>She hated him, he wanted her;</p> <p>she was too good to be true.</p> <p>But a woman can be great â€¦</p> <p>and terrible too.</p> <p><b><i>Wretched</i></b><b> is a dark, contemporary romance (not fantasy or a retelling) and the third complete standalone in The Never After Series: a collection of fractured fairy tales inspired by our favorite villains. It features mature themes and content that may not be suitable for all listeners. Listener discretion is advised.</b></p>"; 
